<p rend="chapter">Ratanattayapaṇāma</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="1"><hi rend="paranum">1</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Mahākavivaraṃ <pb ed="M" n="0.0001" /> buddhaṃ, dhammañca tena sevitaṃ;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Saṅghaṃ niraṅgaṇañcāpi, vandāmi sirasā daraṃ.</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="2"><hi rend="paranum">2</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Karissāmi samāsena, nānāsattha samuddhaṭaṃ;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Hitāya kavinaṃ nītiṃ, kavidappaṇanāmakaṃ.</p>
